[![Edit heuristic-shtern-7ukg9](https://codesandbox.io/static/img/play-codesandbox.svg)](https://codesandbox.io/s/heuristic-shtern-7ukg9?fontsize=14)

and as you can see, the Navbar&#39;s state is set to `Object {name: &quot;Kannan&quot;, countryCode: &quot;&quot;, mobile: &quot;&quot;, isModalOpen: false}`, without the `state` key in it.

